# The 5lb Vow: Nourishment Library

## Breakfast Options
- Avocado Toast with 2 poached eggs and chili flakes.
- Greek Yogurt (unsweetened) with a handful of walnuts and blueberries.
- Scrambled egg whites with spinach, peppers, and feta cheese.

## Lunch Options
- Grilled Salmon over a large bed of mixed greens with lemon-tahini dressing.
- Rotisserie Chicken salad with cucumber, tomato, and balsamic glaze.
- Tuna lettuce wraps with mustard, pickles, and red onion.

## Dinner Options
- Lean Sirloin Steak with roasted asparagus and garlic cauliflower mash.
- Baked Cod with saut√©ed zucchini noodles and pesto.
- Turkey Meatballs over a bed of steamed cabbage or "slaw" (no bun).

## Vow Rules for 5lb Loss
- Protein must be the size of your palm at every meal.
- No processed sugars.
- If you feel snacky, drink 10oz of water first.
